*(Unit → Integration → E2E, GitHub Actions, coverage, alerts)*  

> **Goal** – Guarantee that every push/PR runs the entire test matrix, fails fast, and surfaces issues before a merge.  
> **Scope** – Backend (NestJS + PostgreSQL), Mobile (React Native), Admin Web (React), plus CI‑pipeline and monitoring.

