| **Unit** | 70 % | Jest (Node) + React‑Testing‑Library (RN) | Pure functions, services, validators | `price.calculateTotal`, `auth.service.validateToken` |
| **Integration** | 20 % | Supertest (API), Detox (mobile), Jest (DB layer) | API ↔ DB, auth flow, webhook handling | `POST /orders → DB`, `Stripe webhook → order status` |
